CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 5, 1969, pg. 17 reads: " "Doing Their Thing" - Members of the Milicka Civic Club were caught by photographer "Teenie" Harris "Doing their thing" at their recent "(Dad) Do Your Thing" Cabaret at spacious Rostraver Gardens on Father's Day."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of two women and two men seated behind banquet table in Rostraver Gardens for Milickas Civic Club "Do Your Thing" Cabaret, Belle Vernon
